<% content_for :title do %>Campaigns | <%= installation_brand_name %> User Guide<% end %>
<% content_for :meta_description do %>Proactive live chat, SMS, and WhatsApp campaigns in <%= installation_brand_name %>.<% end %>

<h1>Campaigns</h1>
<p class="lead">
  Campaigns let you reach customers proactively — on your website, via SMS, or WhatsApp templates —
  instead of waiting for inbound messages. Live chat, SMS, and WhatsApp campaigns are included on every plan.
</p>

<h2>Campaign types</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Live chat</strong> — pop-up or targeted message on your website</li>
  <li><strong>SMS</strong> — outbound text to contact lists (Twilio/Bandwidth inbox required)</li>
  <li><strong>WhatsApp</strong> — template-based outbound via connected WhatsApp inbox</li>
</ul>

<h2>Live chat campaigns</h2>
<ol>
  <li><strong>Campaigns → Live chat → Create</strong></li>
  <li>Select website inbox</li>
  <li>Define trigger: URL contains, time on page, exit intent (options vary)</li>
  <li>Write message and optional sender</li>
  <li>Set schedule and audience rules</li>
  <li>Enable and test on staging site first</li>
</ol>
<p>Use for onboarding help, promo offers, or “need assistance?” prompts on checkout pages.</p>

<h2>SMS campaigns</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Connect <a href="<%= guide_page_path('channel-sms') %>">SMS inbox</a> first</li>
  <li><strong>Campaigns → SMS → Create</strong></li>
  <li>Select inbox and audience (labels/segments)</li>
  <li>Compose message; comply with opt-in laws</li>
  <li>Schedule send</li>
</ol>

<h2>WhatsApp campaigns</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Connect <a href="<%= guide_page_path('channel-whatsapp') %>">WhatsApp inbox</a></li>
  <li>Ensure message <strong>template is approved</strong> in Meta WhatsApp Manager</li>
  <li><strong>Campaigns → WhatsApp → Create</strong></li>
  <li>Map template variables and audience</li>
  <li>Schedule within Meta send limits and quality rating</li>
</ol>

<h2>Compliance</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Only message users who opted in</li>
  <li>Honor unsubscribe / STOP requests for SMS</li>
  <li>Follow WhatsApp commerce and template policies</li>
  <li>Document consent in your privacy policy</li>
</ul>

<h2>Measuring results</h2>
<p>Track conversation volume from campaign URLs or labels applied by linked automations. Use <a href="<%= guide_page_path('reports') %>">Reports</a> for broader metrics.</p>

